準，並提出我國公務人員考試方式的改進建議。（25 分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:35:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "393f736fcd78", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113200", "c": "311", "s": "0509", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "公共人力資源管理", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "人事行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-10ced7e2-moex-00065', 'locality-10ced7e2', 'locality-10ced7e2-moex-113-c227590c', 'sub-locality-10ced7e2-01', NULL, 'essay', '不同於企業中的人力資源管理，公共人力資源管理必須包容多元且可能
